<%#Import the header%>
<%- include('templates/header'); -%>
<%#/Import the header%>
<section class="about">
<div class="about-container">
  <div class="about-masthead">
    <h1>Harry and Hermione</h1>
    <time>Written — March 2026</time>
  </div>

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div>
      <h2>About<br> Harry and Hermione</h2>
      <p class="about-hero-text">Harry and Hermione is the ship that never stops sailing. This is a non-for-profit, fan-created website.<br><br></p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-hero-meta">
      <p>By IckleRonnikens</p>
      <p>Images by Hastyhand</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-featured">
    <div class="about-image-placeholder">
      <img src="../images/aboutpage/about.jpg" class="img-fluid w-100">
    </div>
    <p class="about-caption">Harry and Hermione fanart — Drawn by Hastyhand, Feb 2022</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-body-content">
    <div class="about-section-label">Introduction</div>
    <div class="about-body-text">
      <p>The original objective of the website was to create a place on the internet which replaced the void Portkey.org left behind as a whole for fanfiction and forum for discussion based solely on the Harry/Hermione pairing.</p>
      <p>Unforunately, due to unforseen circumstances and lack of knowhow, not everything has worked. The site is what it is, it has it's own identity now. Hopefully, even if one person finds joy from it, or looks at it through rose-coloured glasses, it will have been all worth it.</p>
      <p>Additionally, once you have had a look around, and if by chance you like what you see, or if you have some suggestions as to what could be done better, feel free to leave a comment here: <a href="/feedback"><u>Feedback</u></a>.</p>
    </div>

  </section>

  <section class="about-quote-section">
    <blockquote>
      "Me!" said Hermione. "Books! And cleverness! There are more important things - friendship and bravery and - oh Harry - be careful!"
    </blockquote>
    <p class="about-quote-attribution">— Hermione Granger, The Philosopher's Stone, 1991</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-two-column">
    <div class="about-section-label">Pages</div>
    <div class="about-columns">
      <div class="about-column-text">
        <p><a href="/fanfiction">Fanfiction</a>: Was to be a place where authors could post their HHR stories. The stories would be sorted by readers using a search function similar to what porkey and the archive have (by genres, pairings, rating, and length, options such as including "favorites" are also a possibility).</p>

        <p><a href="/fanart">Fanart</a>: A section called the “Gallery” would be dedicated to posting fan art and where artists can receive comments for their work</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-column-text">
        <p><u>Forum</u>: As the spiritual successor of the portkey website, we would also try to emulate the forum and its subsections within our own forum.</p>
        <p>Quotes: A page dedicated to the best Harry and Hermione quotes in the book and movie franchises.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-image-grid">
    <div class="about-grid-image">
      <img src="../images/aboutpage/01.jpg" alt="Grid image 1">
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid-image">
      <img src="../images/aboutpage/02.jpg" alt="Grid image 2">
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid-image">
      <img src="../images/aboutpage/03.jpg" alt="Grid image 3">
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="about-footer">
    <p>About Page</p>
    <p>Harry and Hermione</p>
  </div>
</div>
</section>


<%#Import the footer%>
